					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"仁浦", "Hitoura"},
					"“This little fellow told me, that’s all. What kind of governor would I be if I can’t even handle a single bird?”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"仁浦"},
					"“为什么？我刚刚才问过这孩子。你连一只鸟都搞不定，就更别说是当县知事的事了──”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
